OL,3,CWidower says he would 'swap money for
OL,4,Cwife back' after #1 million settlement
OL,6,FA widower has told ITV News Central he
OL,7,Fwishes he could swap money to have his
OL,8,Fwife back, after receiving a one
OL,9,Fmillion pound settlement in damages
OL,10,Ffor her death.
OL,12,FRose Fuentebaja, a 40-year-old mother-
OL,13,Fof-three from Stratford-upon-Avon, had
OL,14,Fworked as a nurse for 16 years.
OL,16,FShe was hospitalised for a week
OL,17,Fexperiencing numerous blackouts and
OL,18,Fundergoing multiple ECG tests before
OL,19,Fshe suffered a cardiac arrest and died.
