OL,6,FThe medical team failed to diagnose
OL,7,Fher life-threatening irregular heart
OL,8,Frhythm, mistakenly attributing her
OL,9,Fsymptoms to a neurological issue
OL,10,Finstead of a cardiac problem.
OL,12,FFollowing legal action against West
OL,13,FMidlands Ambulance Service University
OL,14,FNHS Foundation Trust and South
OL,15,FWarwickshire NHS Foundation Trust, a
OL,16,F#1 million damages settlement was
OL,17,Fawarded to her widow, Darrel
OL,18,FFuentebaja.
