OL,6,FThe legal case was led by medical
OL,7,Fnegligence specialists Hudgell
OL,8,FSolicitors.
OL,10,FRose first became ill on May 23, 2017,
OL,11,Fwhen she fainted at home. An ambulance
OL,12,Fcrew performed an ECG test that showed
OL,13,Fdisturbances in her heartbeat but
OL,14,Fattributed it to anxiety and advised
OL,15,Fshe did not need hospitalisation.
