OL,6,FThe next day, she experienced pins and
OL,7,Fneedles in her hands and feet and
OL,8,Ffainted again. This time, she was
OL,9,Ftaken to the hospital, but after an
OL,10,Fassessment, she was sent home as the
OL,11,Fcause could not be determined.
OL,13,FOver the following week, Rose fainted
OL,14,Fseveral more times and was taken to
OL,15,Fthe hospital, where multiple ECG tests
OL,16,Fcontinued to show disturbances in her
OL,17,Fheartbeat. However, she was not placed
OL,18,Funder continuous heart monitoring and
OL,19,Fwas transferred to the neurological
OL,20,Fdepartment at Coventry Hospital.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
