OL,3,CWidower says he would 'swap money for
OL,4,Cwife back' after #1 million settlement
OL,6,FShe was found unresponsive by a nurse
OL,7,Fon June 4 2017 and died of cardiac
OL,8,Farrest despite resuscitation attempts.
OL,10,FAs part of the legal proceedings, West
OL,11,FMidlands Ambulance Service University
OL,12,FNHS Foundation Trust admitted to
OL,13,Fbreaching its duty of care by failing
OL,14,Fto identify potential cardiac issues
OL,15,Fdespite the ECG results and her loss
OL,16,Fof consciousness.
OL,18,FThey also acknowledged that Rose
OL,19,Fshould have been advised to go to the
OL,20,Fhospital on the day of her first
OL,21,Ffainting incident.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
