OL,6,F"Unfortunately, when the time came
OL,7,Fwhen she needed that help, she was
OL,8,Ffailed and it cost her life.
OL,10,F"I went into a deep depression for
OL,11,Fabout a year, and I had a lot of worry
OL,12,Fat that time. I worried about what
OL,13,Fwould happen to my children if
OL,14,Fsomething was to happen to me. I was
OL,15,Fleft feeling very angry and bitter
OL,16,Fabout that, and the mistakes that were
OL,17,Fmade, and that is why I pursued legal
OL,18,Faction for her. I wanted justice for
OL,19,Fher.
